{"tid":756620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美大使館爆炸)    中國外交部：孤立的治安事件","createTime":"2018-07-26T07:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T07:50:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec469868e526db420bfaed1b7464268acadb7f7","tid":756620,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"中共外交部發言人耿爽回應說，你可能已經注意到了，北京警方已在網上發布消息介紹了目前的一些情況，「我想說的是，這起發生在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路的事件是一起孤立的治安事件，中國警方已經即時地、妥善地進行了處理。」<br />\n<br />\n據北京公安官方微博「@平安北京」消息，7月26日下午1時許，一男子在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路十字路口，點燃一疑似爆竹裝置後，發生爆燃，導致其手部受傷，無生命危險。附近巡邏民警迅速開展處置，將該男子控制並送醫治療，現場無其他人員受傷。經查，該男子姜某某，26歲，內蒙古通遼人。目前，警方正在進一步工作中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/07/26/realtime/5048138.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5048138.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=3ccfed86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3274029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3274029&d=MxhcFY12pvSLY75UTrpJRW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ca32b293\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3274029</a>"},{"pid":"1e14e0dea58104c83bfc55bf27e4971ec17680fc","tid":756620,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"這起發生在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路的事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4abc4d897c08e72c46d75131d6a6787d37d8be","tid":756620,"uid":181655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"義x團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6b26e18fe4b3a412e6e75939c224c56209e